org.eclipse.swt.graphics.Drawable
public class OptionsComposite
extends org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Composite

This class draws the three important Widgets for an option and keeps them together and accessible. The three GUI components of an OptionsComposite are a Label showing what option this Composite represents; a Text showing the current value of this option and a Button for resetting the option to its default. Finally, there is a link to the Option: the back end representation of an option. This class is a subclass of Composite
